13

15
16#include "api/neteq/neteq_controller.h"
17
18namespace webrtc {
19
20// Creates NetEqController instances using the settings provided in the config
21// struct.
22class NetEqControllerFactory {
23 public:
24 virtual ~NetEqControllerFactory() = default;
25
26 // Creates a new NetEqController object, with parameters set in |config|.

31} // namespace webrtc
